						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone fixed as arch-stone at the top of the front gate way of the Śaṅkaraliṅga temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>13th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This fragmentary record, in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">13th Century A.D.,</hi> refers to year 20. It mentions the boundaries of a gift land. It also registers a gift of land to god Paṅchaliṅgadēva. The details are lost. </p>						

